# intent/

Core project artifacts directory for Intent v2.9.0 (Agentic Software Engineering Suite). Organizes steel threads (work units), technical documentation, LLM guidance, session tracking, and Claude integration plugins that drive development.

## Dirs

- `analysis/` -- Cost analysis, metrics, and agentic leverage calculations
- `autopsy/` -- Session analysis reports tracking rule enforcement and corrections
- `docs/` -- Technical documentation: rules library, critics, extensions, TCA guide, blog, releases
- `eng/` -- Engineering specifications: treeindex design, agents architecture, implementation details
- `llm/` -- LLM guidance: MODULES.md (Highlander enforcer), DECISION_TREE.md (code placement), AGENTS.md
- `plugins/` -- Claude Code integration: subagents, skills, upgrade utilities, rule schema
- `st/` -- Steel threads: completed work (COMPLETED/), planned (NOT-STARTED/), active ST0034
- `usr/` -- User-facing documentation: guides, reference, deployment, installation

## Files

- `wip.md` -- Current work tracking, active steel threads, and next-up priorities
- `AGENTS.md` -- Development environment, build/test commands, code style, commit guidelines
- `restart.md` -- Session restart snapshot: current state, recent commits, deferred work
- `done.md` -- Completed steel threads and historical autopsy findings
